OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776041695
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has refused to join
OL,7,FDonald Trump's blockade of the Strait
OL,8,Fof Hormuz, which could compound
OL,9,Feconomic pain for Britons with higher
OL,10,Fpetrol costs.
OL,12,FThe president threatened stop tankers
OL,13,Ffrom entering or leaving the key oil
OL,14,Fand gas shipping lane, a move that is
OL,15,Fexpected to further drive up oil
OL,16,Fprices when markets open, after they
OL,17,Fhave already risen as a result of
OL,18,FIran's grip on the strait in
OL,19,Fretaliation for the US-Israel war
OL,20,Fagainst it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
