OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776041695
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FMPs return to Westminster from the
OL,7,FEaster recess on Monday with no
OL,8,Fresolution to the Middle East crisis
OL,9,Fin sight and the fate of a shaky two-
OL,10,Fweek ceasefire uncertain.
OL,12,FMr Trump announced the shipping
OL,13,Fblockade after US-Iranian peace talks
OL,14,Fin Pakistan ended without a deal, with
OL,15,Fboth sides blaming each other.
OL,17,FThe American leader said on his Truth
OL,18,FSocial platform that the US military
OL,19,Fwould start "blockading any and all
OL,20,Fships trying to enter, or leave, the
OL,21,FStrait of Hormuz".
OL,26,@{D@MOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
