OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776041695
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FMr Trump added, without elaborating:
OL,7,F"Other Countries will be involved with
OL,8,Fthis Blockade."
OL,10,FBritain will not be involved, it is
OL,11,Funderstood.
OL,13,FThe UK is "urgently working with
OL,14,FFrance and other partners to put
OL,15,Ftogether a wide coalition to protect
OL,16,Ffreedom of navigation," a Government
OL,17,Fspokesperson said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@OO]uD@KOUxD@WO]
