OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FSir Keir and French President Emmanuel
OL,7,FMacron agreed on the need to work with
OL,8,Fa broad coalition of partners on the
OL,9,Fmatter in a call, according to No 10.
OL,11,FBritain will host further talks on
OL,12,Freopening the maritime pinch-point
OL,13,Fwith a coalition of countries this
OL,14,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
