OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FThe third such meeting convened by the
OL,7,FUK is expected to look for ways to
OL,8,Fsupport a sustainable end to the
OL,9,Fconflict and focus on increasing
OL,10,Finternational diplomatic pressure on
OL,11,FIran to reopen the strait, including
OL,12,Fthrough sanctions.
OL,14,FSir Keir's call with Mr Macron on
OL,15,FSunday took place before Mr Trump
OL,16,Fposted on social media about a
OL,17,Fblockade, it is understood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
