OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776041695
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FMr Trump told Fox News "the UK and a
OL,7,Fcouple of other countries are sending
OL,8,Fmine sweepers" to the strait, and "it
OL,9,Fwon't take long to clean it out".
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister previously said UK
OL,12,Fmine hunting systems were already in
OL,13,Fthe region. But this is thought to
OL,14,Frefer to minesweeping drones which
OL,15,Fcould be deployed once the situation
OL,16,Fstabilises, and to be distinct from Mr
OL,17,FTrump's blockade.
