OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776041695
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FUS Central Command, which is
OL,7,Fresponsible for American military
OL,8,Foperations in the Middle East, said
OL,9,Fits blockade of Iranian ports would
OL,10,Fbegin on Monday.
OL,12,FUS forces "will not impede freedom of
OL,13,Fnavigation for vessels transiting the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz to and from non-
OL,15,FIranian ports," the military said in a
OL,16,Fstatement that appeared to contradict
OL,17,FMr Trump's threat to stop all ships.
OL,26,@tD@KOUwD@OO]
