OL,3,CStarmer refuses to join Trump's Hormuz
OL,4,Cblockade as oil prices expected to rise
OL,6,FThe president blamed the failure of
OL,7,Fnegotiations on Iran's refusal to
OL,8,Freopen the channel and commit to
OL,9,Fgiving up its nuclear ambitions.
OL,11,FIran's foreign minister Abbas Araghchi
OL,12,Faccused Washington of "maximalism,
OL,13,Fshifting goalposts, and blockade,"
OL,14,Fadding: "Enmity begets enmity."
